{"tid":1643575,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工處呼籲僱主因應交通及路面情況彈性安排僱員下班","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:28:09.000Z","uid":274330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48ceb5195f049e2ed644e65a5208e05611890ee0","tid":1643575,"uid":274330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"勞工處呼籲僱主因應交通及路面情況彈性安排僱員下班<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  勞工處今日（十月十日）呼籲僱主，在考慮交通及路面情況後，如有需要，就僱員下班的安排作出彈性處理，這有助維持良好的勞資關係及確保僱員安全。<br />\n   <br />\n  勞工處發言人說：「僱主應因應交通及路面情況，彈性安排僱員下班，讓需要乘坐公共交通公具的員工可順利回家。僱主並應體諒僱員的個別情況而作出彈性處理。」<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年10月10日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間15時00分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/10/P2019101000371.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F10%2FP2019101000371.htm&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em28KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=33b74551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/10/P2019101000371.htm</a>"},{"pid":"397f7ac942d0b931dcc0532b3f14dfa1d42a729c","tid":1643575,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"引用緊急法再講啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a78af8975dd38491a675d63606070611239f788","tid":1643575,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"呢d又唔用緊急法 屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"584ec7e166d25d591e761943f129e30a24a310bc","tid":1643575,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"提早叫人收工慶祝雙十國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63243fa69b2073488725e75af141c4c733d4fd6","tid":1643575,"uid":99505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"又會今日突登出段新聞稿咁講既&hellip;<br />\n真係關雙十事?"},{"pid":"54b01a328c6ce414a1a1933af0575c682b27c73f","tid":1643575,"uid":271581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:28:09.000Z